To build this project using ant, you must place the
following REQUIRED LIBRARIES inside the libs directory
(they are part of the leJOS distribution):
  bluecove.jar or bluecove-2.1.0.jar
  bluecove-gpl.jar
  pccomm.jar
  pctools.jar
  jtools.jar
  jinput.jar
  
-------------------------------------------------------
  
To use a controller (gamepad) you need
the following files:
  Windows:
	jinput-dx8.dll
	jinput-dx8_64.dll
	jinput-raw.dll
	jinput-raw_64.dll
	jinput-wintab.dll
  Linux:
	libjinput-linux.so
	libjinput-linux64.so
  OSX:
	libjinput-osx.jnilib
	
Remember to put them to your VM arguments.
